        <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Write for your audience</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    <p>Content design makes things easier for people to understand and use. Using data, research and testing to understand what people need and then design content to meet those needs.</p>
        <p>Write in plain English and explain complex words and abbreviations.</p>
        <p>Consider what your words mean or how they can be interpreted or translated, think about users whose first language isn't English.</p>
    </div>
